---
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---
<SiteLayout page="acerca" lang="en" title="About — Danilo Diez">

  <div class="about-intro">
    <div class="about-intro-text">
      <h1 class="about-name">Danilo Diez</h1>
      <p class="about-tagline">Engineer, would-be philosopher, product builder, hopelessly curious.</p>
      <p class="about-prose">
        Mate drinker 🧉. Reader 📚. Hacker 💻. I live in Posadas, Misiones, a city on the
        edge of the map, where Argentina meets Brazil and Paraguay.
        I work at <a href="https://webflow.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Webflow</a>
        building web and AI products.
        Outside of work, I co-founded
        <a href="https://somoscool.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cool Studio</a> together with two friends, and I spend
        time on my own projects like <a href="https://salvapatas.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SalvaPatas</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="about-prose">
        Labels are hard for me. I'm an engineer, but I think a lot about the art behind everything.
        I care about products, and also about philosophy and the history of thought.
        I'm driven to create — from complex systems to elaborate dishes for people I love.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-intro-photo">
      <img src="/acerca.jpeg" alt="Danilo Diez in Lauterbrunnen, Switzerland" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Full-width timeline -->
  <section class="about-section about-wide">
    <h2 class="about-section-title">Where I've been</h2>
    <div class="timeline">

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-meta">
          <span class="timeline-year">2026 — present</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <p class="timeline-role">Software Engineer</p>
          <p class="timeline-place"><a href="https://webflow.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Webflow</a></p>
          <p class="timeline-desc">Democratizing the web for creators. Using AI to empower companies, agencies and entrepreneurs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-meta">
          <span class="timeline-year">2025 — present</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <p class="timeline-role">Co-founder</p>
          <p class="timeline-place"><a href="https://somoscool.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cool Studio</a></p>
          <p class="timeline-desc">A web agency I co-founded together with two friends. The goal is simple: build things that are fun for us, for clients that matter.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-meta">
          <span class="timeline-year">2021 — 2026</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <p class="timeline-role">Senior Software Engineer · Lead AI Research</p>
          <p class="timeline-place"><a href="https://leniolabs.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Improving (prev. LenioLabs)</a></p>
          <p class="timeline-desc">I architected micro-frontend systems, led internal AI research, and built agentic workflows with LLMs and voice-recognition products — among them Vocale.ai — for global clients.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-meta">
          <span class="timeline-year">2021</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <p class="timeline-role">Software Developer</p>
          <p class="timeline-place">42Mate — Chaco, Argentina</p>
          <p class="timeline-desc">I developed the full-stack architecture of the History Channel website. I automated migrations with Bash that cut a 3-day task down to seconds.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-meta">
          <span class="timeline-year">2018 — 2021</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <p class="timeline-role">IT Admin</p>
          <p class="timeline-place">Corralón Casía — Corrientes, Argentina</p>
          <p class="timeline-desc">I managed inventory databases and point-of-sale systems across multiple branches.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-meta">
          <span class="timeline-year">Meanwhile…</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <p class="timeline-role">My own projects</p>
          <p class="timeline-place">Various</p>
          <p class="timeline-desc">SalvaPatas, Zona Segura, Anfitrio, landing pages and more landing pages, Vocale, among others. I build when something feels like it should exist.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section about-historia">
    <h2 class="about-section-title">A bit of history</h2>
    <div class="about-historia-grid">
      <div class="about-historia-text">
        <p class="about-prose">
          I was born and raised in Saladas, Corrientes, a town of 20,000 where the passions that move me today were cultivated. Books, film, breaking computers and loving nature.
          I studied systems engineering because I like understanding how complex systems work.
          Along the way I discovered that what interested me most was the power to create what was in my imagination — and if I could do it with friends, even better.
        </p>
        <p class="about-prose">
          I'm studying for a degree in Philosophy. I arrived a little later, through the back door.
          Although I had a lot of influence from an early age — my dad, a philosophy teacher, and my mom cultivated my love of reading.
          What really pushed me to study it was working so closely with language models.
          I want to understand all I can about the human mind, consciousness, and what makes us fundamentally different from this new paradigm of existence.
        </p>
        <p class="about-prose">
          Aside from that, I graduated as a chef, I write, I play guitar, I play basketball and padel, and I love getting lost in the mountains so I can find myself. I can also talk about film for hours.
        </p>
        <p class="about-prose">
          This site is my digital garden.
          A place where I can lay out ideas, projects and things that feed my curiosity.
          Perfection is the enemy of progress.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-historia-photo">
        <img src="/ninio.jpg" alt="As a kid, with a computer in the workshop at home" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="about-body">
    <section class="about-section about-contact">
      <h2 class="about-section-title">Contact</h2>
      <p class="about-prose">
        You can write to me at <a href="mailto:daniloo10.dd@gmail.com">daniloo10.dd@gmail.com</a>, find me on <a href="https://github.com/danilodiez" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>, read me on <a href="https://substack.com/@danilodiez" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Substack</a>, or connect on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/danilodiez/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>. If you prefer, you can <a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">download my CV</a> directly.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>

</SiteLayout>

<style>
  .about-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .about-intro-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-name {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 52px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .about-tagline {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-body {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .about-section-title {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-prose {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 21px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-prose a {
    color: var(--accent-text);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--accent-muted);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color 0.15s, text-decoration-color 0.15s;
  }
  .about-prose a:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .about-historia-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-historia-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 780px) {
    .about-historia-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-historia-photo {
      max-width: 260px;
    }
  }

  /* Full-width timeline */
  .about-wide {
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 160px 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .timeline-meta { padding-top: 3px; }

  .timeline-year {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .timeline-role {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .timeline-place {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .timeline-place a {
    color: var(--accent-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .timeline-place a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  .timeline-desc {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  @media (max-width: 780px) {
    .about-intro { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .about-intro-photo { order: -1; max-width: 280px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .about-name { font-size: 38px; }
    .timeline-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0.2rem; }
  }
</style>
